item.dc:creator: @n33bz0rpl0x `Aaron
item.description:
@n33bz0rpl0x wrote:

[quote=“Fox0wnage, post:2, topic:298595”]There are several things that could’ve happened.

  1. You maybe didn’t save.
  2. (Not very usual but…) Maybe you should try compiling then running again.
  3. You were maybe editing while your player was online. (Before saving make sure the player is offline.)

If it wasn’t any of these reply and tell me.[/quote]

You don’t have to compile them, EVER.
